{"tid":1245094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長期抗爭需要一篇類似禱文嘅嘢鞏固信念","createTime":"2019-06-20T07:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T07:27:06.000Z","uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ab14574d9176072d3b7aae9c09987c84259e31dc","tid":1245094,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢，政府會盡量令到網絡上面資訊疲勞<br />\n人都係血肉之軀<br />\n每一個記者會，每一件荒唐嘅新聞<br />\n都會令到所有參與者少一分耐性<br />\n令到坊間不知不覺間淡化對事情嘅關注度<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以參考基督徒咁樣嘅運作方式<br />\n以靈性修練或者祈禱嘅方式不斷提醒自己<br />\n呢一場戰鬥終極並且唯一嘅目標係乜嘢<br />\n而每一個行動，或和理非或衝<br />\n都係指向果一個目標<br />\n<br />\n大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tAPVh4S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtAPVh4S.png&h=7dcfa4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7KJyPbx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7KJyPbx.png&h=5773ea12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0FmdDc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0FmdDc.png&h=d1d65880&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQAJrYd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQAJrYd.png&h=0cdfa708&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}